codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand latin grammar. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. Dominus servum laudat quod industriē labōrāv~. Choose from this set of possible answers [ it, erat, erit, ērunt, erant, erint] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-babbage-001' where ANSWER in [ 'it', 'erat', 'erit', 'ērunt', 'erant', 'erint']
